{"tid":857458,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選香港邊區最多廢老","createTime":"2018-10-11T06:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:38:22.000Z","uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c3814bb23b784d0a763a5c1f869f5ac6f4479143","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"成日見到啲廢老朝早係地鐵門口排隊拎報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阻撚住啲人翻工翻學<br />\n見到隔離po又話廢老聚集係M記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係到諗香港邊區最多廢老係到阻街<br />\n例如係坐係大家樂/商場成日咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港島: <br />\n中西區 <br />\n東區 <br />\n南區 <br />\n灣仔 <br />\n<br />\n九龍: <br />\n九龍城 <br />\n油尖旺 <br />\n深水埗 <br />\n黃大仙 <br />\n觀塘 <br />\n<br />\n新界: <br />\n大埔 <br />\n屯門 <br />\n元朗 <br />\n北區 <br />\n西貢 <br />\n沙田 <br />\n荃灣 <br />\n葵青"},{"pid":"d4984bdca6187a7b9a947393d0c46ac9050e47e8","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"個人記為黃大仙都幾多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6007efc1367ff0c29c9a28d67a0c4acf17dd6af2","tid":857458,"uid":177399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"柴灣"},{"pid":"965d46468747d2a764f1e89dff3bc82a0797985a","tid":857458,"uid":32951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ecf66b1695d821c360d0d32c879645ebda3405","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6007efc1367ff0c29c9a28d67a0c4acf17dd6af2","tid":857458,"uid":177399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"柴灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"舊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a4543a46f147157c6ea44399898ad5012b45a4","tid":857458,"uid":61332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得深水埗都絕對有力一戰"},{"pid":"152245634e84a88e1337c04af655432725bcea6d","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"2015立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n本港人口老化問題教人關注。統計處公布2014年的分區人口資料，發現全港年齡中位數較2013年再升一歲至42歲。其中<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃大仙及東區繼續成為本港的「老人區」</span>，年齡中位數高達45歲。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計處公布2014年分區人口及住戶統計資料，2014年全港人口的年齡中位數為42歲，比2013年上升了一歲。其中黃大仙及東區成為老化問題最嚴重的地區，年齡中位數達45歲。黃大仙65歲或以上的長者比例高達17.7，為全港長者比例最高的地區。東區的長者比例則為17.3。南區、深水埗、觀塘、葵青四個地區中位數為43歲，同樣高於全港水平。最年輕的區域為元朗及離島，年齡中位數為39歲。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在住戶每月入息中位數排名中，全港最窮的區域為深水埗，住戶入息中位數為1.8萬元。觀塘排名第二，中位數為1.9萬元。中西區住戶入息中位數最高，為3.5萬元。其次為灣仔區，入息中位數達34,000元"},{"pid":"2e4b1eacae4dc34da234e6153b2736981173512d","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a4543a46f147157c6ea44399898ad5012b45a4","tid":857458,"uid":61332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得深水埗都絕對有力一戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 深水埗啲廢老日日見到啲蝻有咩感覺"},{"pid":"9a3cd52243437344a17f1b3f2bcb8dd1e6c798db","tid":857458,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"葵青"},{"pid":"9cd82cc01b1bf64d1bce09870560978fbb1135fc","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"好似愈窮既地區愈多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d647151361b69f47d4c1ec6479418d6ebffe95","tid":857458,"uid":143380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"