3.000Z","msg":"東區咁多廢老但家庭入息中位數排頭5喎"},{"pid":"41c0a8042124db4f3b09c1f0653fdc2ce7bd75d7","tid":857458,"uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"邊到都好啦，班死廢老蠶食三代人既資源，攞儘曬著數，仲要日日係到奶共，陷害下一代。班廢老好應該捉曬去填海，打生椿，祭海豚。"},{"pid":"4c35aab6662d39bc41ee37eab6bc155ade316b47","tid":857458,"uid":207462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"唔使講一定係黃大仙<br />\n成日落街食早餐都聽到佢地話政府咁好班後生做咩係咁反<br />\n心諗你地上晒岸有樓住福利又多梗係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好幾次經過樓下公園見到有啲廢老喺度同啲師奶打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而深水埗多老人家但本身唐樓多<br />\n真係有唔少公公婆婆勉強過活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbde0e5f613a72bf946992d168c5c64ceabcfa0","tid":857458,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e6f9da568e2590ce684d282f831ce6f0b789fcf3","tid":857458,"uid":97071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:34:39.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗 廢老樂園"},{"pid":"5f9cbed38c2d95bc3de77fa8a3d88ee466592d56","tid":857458,"uid":216664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"廢老唔係靠年齡定義，而係靠思想。問題唔係人口老化，而係上一代好多人都靠經濟起飛搵食，淨係識屌依家嘅年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7d674381931cabf5ff354510cdc97d479971ac","tid":857458,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f9cbed38c2d95bc3de77fa8a3d88ee466592d56","tid":857458,"uid":216664,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"廢老唔係靠年齡定義，而係靠思想。問題唔係人口老化，而係上一代好多人都靠經濟起飛搵食，淨係識屌依家嘅年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"